As a little note (and I'm not doing this to be obnoxious), I thought I'd include the dictionary definitions I looked up for nationalism and ethnicity. I don't want to end up disagreeing when we actually agree just because we're understanding the meaning of the same words we use differently. If you think the definitions are incomplete or wrong, fine. Just know that when I use the words, these definitions are what I'm going by. I realize that words take on a life of their own and sometimes have different conotations for different people, but I try (keyword, try) to use them consistenly to reduce confusion.<br>
